Docker - its an open source platform for managing and running containers


 - Container RUN time

Docker
RKT
Containerd - kubernetes is using containerd run time


docker hub ---- docker images 

-----------------------------
Installation of docker 


yum install docker 

systemctl status docker
systemctl start docker

docker pull ubuntu

docker run -it ubuntu 

cat /etc/os-release

exit  - comes out of container by exiting the container
-------------------------------------------------

docker pull centos

docker run -it --name container-centos centos

cat /etc/os-release



ctrl P + ctrl q -- to come out of the container without exiting container

